rrister - or it was more, I should think, clerical than anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3035053 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 He worked in the offices there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10227369 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 Yes. But I think he was one of - he was garrulous and I think he would rather have got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8196131 
Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511  and lived a useless life than what he had and he did do. That hence his dying at 46 in the Pub.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3035053 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 Now did he have any job before or after he worked on the Newspaper as a clerk, did he have any other jobs at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10227369 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 Well, I wouldn't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3035053 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 You don't know that, right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10227369 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 Because that's before my time. I don't think so, I think he came right from Manchester and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3035053 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 Now do you remember your father ever being out of work? I know you probably won't remember it.
