\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3035053 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 I see. So he wasn't likely to have been out of work?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10227369 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3035053 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 No. Quite. Now how old was your mother when you were born? Was she younger or older than your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10227369 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 I fancy she was older, myself, a little.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3035053 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 You would?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10227369 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 I would say so.
