\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10227369 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 Look, it was like rumoured that she'd given her wrong age at the wedding.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3035053 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 I see, so what would you say yourself, about 37ish you think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10227369 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 Probably.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3035053 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 Now, where did she come from, your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10227369 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 Scotland.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3035053 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 A Scotswoman?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10227369 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3035053 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 And had she any jobs before she }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8196131 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 , do you know.?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10227369 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 Oh, yes. Well, she came to - what she d
id in Scotland I don't know - but at an early age of 18 or something she came to Liverpool, and in no time she was manageress of Waterloo Hotel in Clayton Square, which is Moores now, the sale people. She was manageress at that, and I don't know but - why
 she left it. She bought or she got this free house in Lawton Street. It was here own really because it was untied and ......
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3035053 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 Quite. So she could do what she liked with it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10227369 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 So she - and when she want there I don't know whether she }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8196131 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511  a Mr Whitfield before she went there from the Waterloo, or after, it must have been before she }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8196131 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511  a Mr Whitfield, but he died at an early age and she had no life with him but that would have been a happy marriage, had he lived. She had one child, her and he, but that child died. Then she }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8196131 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511  this .....
