\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10227369 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 Not so very good. Had no work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3035053 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 Never mind. So long as it didn't affect you it didn't obviously.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10227369 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 It didn't affect me but my mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3035053 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 I'm sure it did. Now she did work after she was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8196131 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 , she worked continuing managing the Pub, the boarding house and the chip shop. Did she do anything else after that when she went back to the boarding house from where you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
