\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10227369 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3035053 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 No? Now, did your mother pay anyone to help in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10227369 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 She had to pay for the pub.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3035053 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 Yes. But she didn't pay anyone to help her clean up and help in the house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10227369 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 Yes, she had a woman and came in daily like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3035053 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 Fine. Now, what were her duties? Did she do the cleaning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10227369 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 Cleaning, make the beds.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3035053 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 Did she look after you at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10227369 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3035053 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 No?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10227369 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 Only in the pub, the public house, we had a maid that used to bath me as a child like and ......
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3035053 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 Right. Now
, how did you get on with this daily help, woman who came in daily, can you remember her? What she called you and what she called your mother? Did she call you by any name, your own.
