\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3035053 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 Really? In this fire range?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10227369 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3035053 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 But she had a gas stove as well?
