My father get hold of their heads and screw their neck and draw them down. And then my mother would make pigeon pie or. She used to buy rabbits but ......
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3035053 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 Not have them, not poached? Do you remember }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1595690\charrsid13375511 seeing}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511  your mother having less food so that the family could have more? And did your father have more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10227369 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 No.
