\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10227369 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 As far as I know, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3035053 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 Could you choose what you wanted to eat from what was cooked or did you have to eat a bit of everything?
