\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10227369 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3035053 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 Now did you go out in the evening at all when you started working?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10227369 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 Oh yes - I went out in the evenings with the - I might - er - make a - meet two or three young friends, like, and we used to wander the
 streets singing in harmony - we all had good voices - we were all choir boys - choir men, like - choir boys, like - I was in the - at one time I was in the - as I told you - Seamen's Institute - for Seamen, like - and - er - we used to spend our time sin
g
ing. I had two sets of company, like - these and more intimate friends where I used - we used to go to their houses of each and - and every evening through the week was a party - sort of thing - a sing-song - one - one could play the piano and - then we w
ould - er - have - join in and tea and sandwiches at different homes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3035053 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 This was something you did very }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11810004\charrsid13375511 often}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10227369 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7230018\charrsid13375511 Yes - as a young man.
