Oh I don't know - I mean to say - one girl I used to - we used to go - er - that was when I was working in Prescot - I had - I took out a girl although she was - atta
ched to someone else in Blackpool where she was a maid but for her spare time I used to take her out in Prescot - we used to go to the Theatre Royal in St Kevins and there was a Charlie Chaplin such a thing as - after this - after the show that left me la
te and - miss the last bus and had to - get a taxi back.
